        <caption>
          <p><bold>Computed background vs. low expressed genes data</bold>. Experimental results (solid black line) and theoretical prediction (dashed red line) of probeset a) 256610_at (A. Thaliana, GSE4847, GSM109107.CEL) and b) 175270_at (C. Elegans, GSE8159, GSM201995.CEL).</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="1748-7188-4-15-5"/>
      </fig>
    </sec>
